      "text": "Brave: Shaman's Challenge is a puzzle video game by American developer Collision Studios that was planned for release for the Nintendo DS in North America and PAL regions in early 2009. The game is a spin-off of the PlayStation 2 platformer Brave: The Search for Spirit Dancer. Brave, the main character, has to use quick thinking and magic spells to battle Shamans terrorizing him in his dreams. The game was however cancelled.",
